frames.caption: A surreal scene depicts tiny skiers navigating a snowy slope that is creatively formed on a peeled banana. The banana is set against a soft, cloudy sky, adding to the whimsical atmosphere. The skiers appear to be enjoying their descent, with one reaching the peak of the banana's curve.
frames.description: The image presents a playful and imaginative setting where a banana is transformed into a ski slope. The scene combines elements of nature with a touch of fantasy, creating a dreamlike landscape.

frames.caption: Two snowboarders glide down a snowy slope, leaving trails of powder in their wake. The scene is set against a backdrop of dramatic ice formations and a cloudy sky.
frames.description: The image captures an exhilarating snowboarding scene on a snowy mountain slope. The snowboarders are navigating a steep descent, surrounded by striking ice formations and a cloudy atmosphere.
